OL,3,CFirst LGBT group to meet Pope hails
OL,4,Chis 'transformative' welcoming approach
OL,6,FA member of a UK-based gay Catholic
OL,7,Fgroup, said to be the first to have
OL,8,Fmet the Pope in Rome, has recalled his
OL,9,F"warmth" and hailed the "radical
OL,10,Ftransformation" in welcoming everyone
OL,11,Finto the Church.
OL,13,FMembers of LGBT+ Catholics Westminster
OL,14,Fshook hands with and had their picture
OL,15,Ftaken with Francis by the Vatican
OL,16,Fphotopaper in an "amazing" surprise
OL,17,Fencounter in 2019.
