OL,4,Chis 'transformative' welcoming approach
OL,6,FThe group's secretary recalled how the
OL,7,FPope had told them, in a brief meeting
OL,8,Fafter a morning audience in St Peter's
OL,9,FSquare, that it was "wonderful" to
OL,10,Fhear they were an officially
OL,11,Frecognised group.
OL,13,FMartin Pendergast, secretary of the
OL,14,Fgroup's pastoral council, said: "It
OL,15,Fwas just amazing. I mean, we couldn't
OL,16,Fbelieve it was happening.
OL,18,F"It was a brief encounter but there
OL,19,Fwas a warmth, and he shook hands with
OL,20,Feverybody.
