OL,6,F"When I explained that we were an
OL,7,Fofficial ministry of the diocese he
OL,8,Fsaid 'that's wonderful, that's
OL,9,Fwonderful'."
OL,11,FAsked about the significance of the
OL,12,Foccasion, Mr Pendergast ` an ordained
OL,13,Fpriest who no longer carries out
OL,14,Factive ministry ` said he believed it
OL,15,Fwas the first time an LGBT group had
OL,16,Fmet and been pictured with the Pope.
