OL,6,FSix years earlier, in his first year
OL,7,Fas head of the Catholic Church, Pope
OL,8,FFrancis was reported to have indicated
OL,9,Fhe would not judge priests for their
OL,10,Fsexual orientation, saying: "If
OL,11,Fsomeone is gay and he searches for the
OL,12,FLord and has good will, who am I to
OL,13,Fjudge?"
OL,15,FThe comment made headlines, standing
OL,16,Fin stark contrast to his predecessor,
OL,17,FPope Benedict XVI, who signed a
OL,18,Fdocument in 2005 that said men with
OL,19,Fdeep-rooted homosexual tendencies
OL,20,Fshould not be priests.
