OL,6,FMr Pendergast said Francis' remark
OL,7,Fshowed a change in attitude.
OL,9,F"I certainly remember the statement.
OL,11,F"The 'who am I to judge?' really was
OL,12,Fthe first time that a pope had even
OL,13,Fused the g-word. So he was the first
OL,14,FPope to actually use the word gay.
OL,16,F"So even the way he speaks has been a
OL,17,Fradical transformation, and some would
OL,18,Fsay, a bit of a revolution as well,
OL,19,Fcompared with some of his
OL,20,Fpredecessors."
