OL,6,FHe was a Pope focused on meeting
OL,7,Fpeople and engaging with them, rather
OL,8,Fthan being too "bothered about the
OL,9,Ftheories, the doctrines, the
OL,10,Fteachings", Mr Pendergast said.
OL,12,FHis approach was a "grassroots" one,
OL,13,Fto "meet people and then to think
OL,14,Fabout where the doctrine, where the
OL,15,Ftheology, might be beginning to change
OL,16,For develop", he added.
