OL,6,FIn December 2023, the Pope formally
OL,7,Fapproved allowing priests to bless
OL,8,Fsame-sex couples, as long as such
OL,9,Fblessings do not give the impression
OL,10,Fof a marriage ceremony, reversing a
OL,11,F2021 policy by the Vatican's doctrine
OL,12,Foffice, which barred such blessings on
OL,13,Fthe grounds that God "does not and
OL,14,Fcannot bless sin".
OL,16,FAsked during a television interview if
OL,17,Fhe felt alone afterwards, Francis
OL,18,Freplied: "You take a decision and
OL,19,Fsolitude is a price you have to pay."
