OL,4,Chis 'transformative' welcoming approach
OL,6,FHe added: "Sometimes decisions are not
OL,7,Faccepted. But in most cases, when you
OL,8,Fdon't accept a decision, it's because
OL,9,Fyou don't understand."
OL,11,FHe warned the danger is that when
OL,12,Fpeople who do not understand something
OL,13,Frefuse to enter into a "brotherly
OL,14,Fdiscussion" and instead harden their
OL,15,Fhearts, resist and "make ugly
OL,16,Fconclusions".
OL,18,FHe added: "This has happened with
OL,19,Fthese last decisions about blessing
OL,20,Feveryone. The Lord blesses everyone."
