OL,6,FMr Pendergast said the Pope had
OL,7,F"trodden fairly carefully" when it
OL,8,Fcame to change in the Church but
OL,9,Fencouraged a more welcoming attitude.
OL,11,FHe said: "I think he's trodden fairly
OL,12,Fcarefully, emphasising not so much a
OL,13,Fchange in teaching documents, but
OL,14,Femphasising the pastoral practice, the
OL,15,Fpastoral welcome, the pastoral
OL,16,Fattitude, has to be much more
OL,17,Fgenerous."
