OL,6,FLast year, an apology was issued on
OL,7,FFrancis' behalf over the use of
OL,8,Flanguage seen as homophobic after a
OL,9,Fremark said to have been made behind
OL,10,Fclosed doors to Italian bishops was
OL,11,Fwidely reported by Italian media.
OL,13,FThe Pope was said to have used the
OL,14,Fterm "frociaggine", considered
OL,15,Fderogatory, when answering no to a
OL,16,Fquestion on whether gay men should be
OL,17,Fadmitted to seminaries to train for
OL,18,Fthe priesthood.
